K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:1b-0: @1b #// 'dul ba gzhung dam pa bam po nyer gsum pa /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:168b-16: las gang yin pas skyes pa ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:168b-18: lha'i bu mo dpal gyi blo gros mas bdag gang nas shi 'phos zhes bltas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:168b-20: gang du snyam pa dang sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i khams bzang por skyes pa mthong ngo; ;las gang yin zhe na /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:168b-23: bdag gis zhag lon nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal lta ba'i mi rigs kyi /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:168b-29: se mo dos brgyan te lha'i me tog autpal dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-0: mand'a ra ba la sogs pa'i me tog dag gis pang ba bkang nas 'od ma'i tshal bya ka landa ka gnas pa @169a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-1: rgya chen pos thams cad 'od snang bar byas te bcom ldan 'das la me tog gis mngon par gtor nas chos nyan pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i bsam pa dang /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-6: des bden pa mthong nas brjod pa bya ba rnam gsum brjod de /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag gi mchi ma dang /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-35: ngan song lam ste nyes mang po //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-36: mtho ris bsod nams sgo yang phye //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-37: mya ngan 'das pa'i lam yang bdag gis thob //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169a-38: khyod la brten nas nyes pa rnams kyang spangs //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-0: bdag @169b gis rtag tu rnam dag mig kyang thob //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-1: 'phags pa dga' zhing zhi ba'i lam yang thob //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-2: sdug bsngal mtsho las pha rol bdag brgal nas //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-3: 'gro ba na yang lha mi rnams kyis mchod //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-4: skye rga na dang 'chi ba'i nyes dang bral //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-5: srid pa stong du'ang rab tu mthong bar dka'/

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:169b-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis der 'od rgya cher snang ba mthong ngo /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:170a-1: kyi; rgyal po gzugs can snying po'i chung ma dpal gyi blo gros ma zhes bya ba zhig gis bdag gi 'tsho ba la ma bltas te de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbu skra dang /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:170a-32: yun ring po nas bsod nams byas pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:170a-33: rnam par smin pa la mos pa dang; sdug pa dang /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:187b-14: 'bras bu dag gi sman byas kyang de'i nad tha gi bar ma gyur nas de na ba'i sdug bsngal gyis ring po mi thogs par dus 'da' bar shes nas des khyim tshes dag bsags te 'dus nas de'i nang du bu la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:187b-16: khyed cag gi bu chen po dge sbyong sh'akya'i sras kyi nang du rab tu byung ba de yang khyed kyis nor skal byin cig ces smras nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:187b-17: bsags pa kun mtha' zad par 'gyur //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-2: chos kyi mtha' ni zhi bar 'gyur //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-3: dus kyi chos dang ldan par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-4: de'i bu ljongs spyod cing 'dug pa des bdag gi pha dus las 'das so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-5: zhes thos te de yang 'di snyam du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-6: bdag song la ma yar mo dang nu bo dag gi mya ngan bsang gi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-8: snyam du sems nas de ji tsam dga' ba'i bar du ljongs spyad de mnyan du yod pa gang na ba de logs su ljongs spyod cing song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-9: rim bzhin du spyod cing mnyan du yod par phyin nas lam gyi ngal bsos te bdag gi khyim du 'ongs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-10: nang gi skye bo dag gis mthong nas ngus te dus pa'i sgra dag khyim tshes dag gis thos nas de dag 'dus te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-14: mig mchi mas gang zhing 'dus nas so so'i skye bo dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-15: 'dod chags dang ldan pas gnyen dang bral bar gyur pa mya ngan gyis mig mchi mas gang ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-16: de yang du ga khyer zhing 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-17: de la rgan mo gzhan zhig gis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-19: khyed kyi phas ni; nor skal byin par nged kun gyis kyang thos na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-24: de cung zad tsam zhig gi bar du sems shing 'dug nas des /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-26: nu bo dag la chos bshad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188a-27: de dag gi mya ngan cung zad sangs nas de dag gis khyod kyi nor skal dag longs shig ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-0: bcom ldan 'das kyis nga 'das nas byin pa @188b ni; med do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-2: ji ltar blang snyam du bsam nas tshe dang ldan pa dag /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-4: rab tu byung ba la nor rdzas kyis byar med kyi steng du bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang nga 'das nas byin pa med do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-6: khyed cag nyid khyer cig ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-7: de dag gis nyes pa ngor brjod pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-9: longs la sbyin pa yang byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-11: de la nyes pa ci zhig yod ces smras so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-12: de ltar gyur pa dge slong dag la smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-13: dge slong dag gis bcom ldan 'das la gsol nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-17: rab tu byung ba la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-18: re ba med pa'i phyir te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-20: nga 'das na byin cig pa na khyim pa dag gi de btsan no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-21: rab tu byung ba la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-24: khyim pas de lta bur bsam ste byin pa longs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-27: dge 'dun la bya ba'i phyir te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-28: de la the tshom du ma byed cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-30: mnyan du yod pa na ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-31: dge slong dag lci ba'i ri lu dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-34: ba lang gi lci ba rnams 'chags dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-36: sgo khang dag tu bor nas ljongs spyad pa spyod du 'dong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-37: de dag la dge slong dag gis the tshom skyes nas ma spyod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-38: de ltar gyur pa dge slong dag gis bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-39: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:188b-40: yid gcugs pa rnam pa lnga las ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-2: thos na dga' bar 'gyur pa ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-3: yid gcugs pa rnam pa de lnga la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-5: de lta the tshom du ma byed cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-7: mnyan du yod pa na ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-8: mnyan du yod pa na khyim bdag gzhan zhig 'dug pa des rigs mnyam pa las chung ma zhig blangs nas de dang lhan cig tu rtse dga' yongs su spyod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-9: de la rtse dga' yongs su spyod pa las dus phyi zhig na chung ma sems can dang ldan par gyur nas de zla ba brgyad dam dgu 'das pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-10: bu mo zhig btsas nas de zhag bdun gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar du btsas pa'i btsas ston chen po byas nas rigs dang mthun pa'i ming btags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-11: de bsrings bskyed de cher gyur pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-12: khyim bdag gzhan zhig gis de bslangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-13: de rdzas la sogs pas de brdzangs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-15: dus phyi zhig na khyim pa de dus 'das nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-16: de khyo dang bral ba'i mya ngan gyis gdungs nas legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-17: de dus phyi zhig na mu ge byung nas bsod snyoms slong zhing 'dug pa dang de bsod snyoms spyod pa las srang zhig tu de'i phas mthong nas des smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-19: da ltar gang na ji ltar 'tsho zhing 'dug ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-21: mu ge byung nas bdag rab tu bkres shing 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-24: de ltar na khyod rab tu ma byung na ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189a-25: ngas khyod la mi 'dod bzhin du sbyin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-0: da bsod snyoms ma @189b byed par bdag gi khyim du zan za zhing dbyar mo khang du song zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-1: des khas blangs nas de grogs shig dang gnyis kyis zos shing dbyar mo khang du song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-2: zhag du ma zhig gi bar du der zos nas bu /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-4: zas sbyin par mi nus kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-5: khyod gcig pu 'dir zan zos shing song zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis gcig pu grong du 'gro bar ma gnang ngo; ;zhes smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-9: de cang mi zer bar 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-10: de ltar gyur pa dge slong ma dag gis dge slong dag la smras pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-11: dge slong dag gis bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-12: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-16: dge slong ma'i dge 'dun la gnyen dang lhan cig 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-19: stan bting la gand'i brdungs te dge slong ma'i dge 'dun dag 'dus shing 'khod pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-20: ji ltar rgan rim du phyag byos la rgan rim gyi mdun du pha gu'am /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-21: stan nang tshangs can gyi steng du 'dug nas thal mo sbyar la tshig 'di skad ces smros shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-22: gson cig 'phags ma'i dge 'dun ma rnams /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-23: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas 'di 'dra ba'i mu ge'i dus la bab nas bsod snyoms blangs ba yang mi nus na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:189b-24: 'phags ma'i dge 'dun ma la bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'phags ma'i dge 'dun ma las gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa gsol na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-1: ma'i dge 'dun dag gis bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la gnyen dang lhan cig 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-2: brtse ba can brtse ba'i phyir ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-3: de ltar lan gnyis lan gsum du brjod par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-4: de'i 'og tu dge slong ma gcig gis gsol ba gyis la las byos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-5: gson cig 'phags ma'i dge 'dun ma rnams /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-6: dge slong ma ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-7: 'di ltar mu ge'i dus la bab ste 'phags ma'i dge 'dun dag las gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa gsol na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-8: de ste 'phags ma'i dge 'dun rnams kyis dus la bab cing bzod na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-9: 'phags ma'i dge 'dun ma rnams kyis gnongs la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-10: 'phags ma'i dge 'dun gyis dge slong ma ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di la gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-15: dge slong ma ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-16: 'di ltar mu ge'i dus la bab ste 'phags ma'i dge 'dun rnams la gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa gsol te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-17: de las 'phags ma'i dge 'dun gyis dge slong ma ming 'di zhes bgyi ba mu ge'i dus la bab na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190a-18: gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa gsol na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-0: 'phags ma rnams las gang la dge @190b slong ma ming 'di zhes bgyi ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-1: mu ge'u dus la bab ste gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa stsol bar bzod pa de dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-5: 'phags ma'i dge 'dun gyis dge slong ma ming 'di zhes bgyi bas gnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa stsal te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-8: dge slong mas mnyen dang lhan cig tu 'dre bar nye spyod kyi sdom pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-9: dge 'dun ma rnams kyis byin par gyur na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-10: gcig pu gnyen gyi khyim du zas za bar gyis la de la the tshom du ma byed cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-11: nam mu ge'i tshe ni; rjes su gnang ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-12: de ma yin par ma gnas shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-13: mu ge ma byung bar gnas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-15: gleng gzhi'i nang nas sgo bzhi pa'i mdo'i tshigs su bcad pa bdun pa'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-17: bskyi ba la ni rnam pa gnyis //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-18: ras la yang ni rnam gsum ste //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-19: nyo bar yang ni 'dod pa dang //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-20: sder bsdus par ni gyur pa'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-21: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das mnyan du yod pa na dze ta'i tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-22: dge slong gzhan zhig gis khyim bdag cig la karsha pa ni zhig bskyis pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-23: de dus kyi mtha' zhig tu ci zhig gis dus 'das nas dge slong de ji ltar dus 'das pa khyim bdag des thos so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:190b-24: dge slong de ji ltar dus 'das pa khyim bdag des thos nas gtsug lag khang du song ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-3: 'di zhes bgyi ba'i dge slong de gang na mchis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-8: des bdag gi karsha pa ni zhig bskyis te 'tshal to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-14: khyed kyis de'i lhung bzed dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-16: bdag gis ji ltar dur khrod du song ste bda'/
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-19: de ltar gyur pa dge slong rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la gsol nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-23: de'i nor las bskyis pa dge slong dag gis byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-24: de dag gis gang nas sbyin pa mi shes nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-26: chos gos yod pa las byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-27: dge slong de dag gis lhung bzed dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-28: chos gos de dag byin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-30: chos gos de dag ma 'dod nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-32: dge slong dag gis de dag thams cad byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-33: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191a-34: ji tsam blangs pa de tsam du byin la lhag ma bgos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-0: mnyan du yod pa na dge slong gzhan zhig gis khyim bdag cig las karsha pa na zhig @191b bskyis pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-1: de dus kyi mtha' zhig tu ci zhig gis dus 'das pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-2: dge slong dag gis snga ma bzhin du lhung bzed dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-3: chos gos btsongs nas de la byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-4: khyim bdag gis smras pa; 'phags pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-5: des bdag la 'di tsam zhig 'tshal te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-10: de ltar gyur pa dge slong rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-12: de la de'i lhung bzed dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-16: de ste yid mi ches na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-17: go bar gyis shig ;go bar bsgo yang mi btub na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-19: gang zag gzhan gyi las ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-21: rigs kyi gzu bo rnams kyis go bar bsgos la thong zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-23: mnyan du yong ba na dge slong zhig gis gos tshong pa las ras shig rin ma byin par blangs pa las /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-24: dge slong de dus 'das nas dge slong de dus 'das so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-25: zhes gos kyi bdag po des thos nas de gtsug lag khang du 'ongs te shes bzhin du dge slong rnams la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-27: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di ga la mchis zhes dris pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-32: des bdag las ras shig rin ma sbyin par byas te khyer ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:191b-34: de dur khrod du bskyal gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-3: bdag ci'i phyir dur khrod du song ste bda'/
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-5: de ltar gyur pa dge slong rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la gsol nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-7: gos tshong pa 'di smra ba ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-11: dge slong rnams kyis de'i ras nyid byin pa dang; des 'phags pa rnams /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-12: bdag la des rin thang 'di tsam du 'tshal to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis de nyid tshongs la byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-16: dge slong rnams kyis de btsong par brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-17: snga ma'i rin thang du ma lon nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-20: lhung bzed rnams tshongs la byin cig; gleng gzhi ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-21: mnyan du yod pa na dge slong zhig gis tha ga pa la ras 'thag pa'i phyir skud pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-22: rngan pa byin pa las dge slong dus 'das nas dge slong rnams kyis tha ga pa la bos te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-24: khyod la dge slong ming 'di zhes bya bas ras 'thag pa'i phyir skud pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-25: rngan pa byin pa de slar phul cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192a-28: bdag gis de la ras sbyin par byas kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-0: dge slong rnams kyis de ji ltar bya ba ma shes nas de ltar gyur pa dge slong rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la @192b gsol ba dang bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-2: tha ga pa smra ba ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-6: dge slong rnams kyis phra mo las bkug pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-8: bdag gis de la sbom po sbyin par byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-13: ji ltar byin pa de lta bur longs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-15: mnyan du yod pa na ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-16: dge slong zhig gis gos tshong pa la karsha pa na byin te ras shig byin cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-18: dge slong de dus 'das nas dge slong rnams kyis gos tshong pa la bos te; bzhin bzang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-19: khyod la dge slong ming 'di zhes bya bas ras kyi rin zhig byi pa de 'on cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:192b-22: de la ras su sbyin par bgyis so //

K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-1: gis zas 'brim pa'i tshe snyoms par brims shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-3: des tshad ma sna re re la'ang smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-5: lan tshva 'am; dang por gang brims pa de'i tshe smros shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-8: dge 'dun gyi gnas brtan dge slong gis ji ltar bur mtshungs par spyad pa'i chos bzhin ma byas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-10: tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag gis zan zos pa smad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-12: zhes thos nas des bdag ston pas zan zes pa smad na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-14: zhes bsam nas des bskyugs te btang ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-16: the tshom skyes nas the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu la zan zos pa smad pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-19: des slar bskyugs pa la gzigs su gsol /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-23: sngon 'das pa'i dus na yang ngas de la zan zos pa la smad pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-27: grong khyer gzhan zhig na mang por 'chad pa'i bram ze zhig gnas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244a-28: de bram ze'i bu dang lhan cig tu ljongs rgyu zhing spyod pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-0: ri brag gi grong zhig tu phyin nas des rdzing zhig gi 'gram du bram ze des bram ze'i bu der bzhag nas cung @244b zad cig sdod /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-1: nga grong du phye la sogs pa bslangs te slar 'ong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-3: khyi sha can zhig rdzing du chu brog 'thung du 'ongs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-4: de la bram ze'i bus kye skyes bu /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-5: bdag kyang chu brog cig stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-7: des kyang lo ma la snod drubs shig ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-9: des de la khyi'i pags pa la byas pa'i sgye'u'i nang nas byung ba'i phye byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-10: de snum pa dang bram ze'i bus phye 'di snum na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-11: ci zhig ces dris pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-13: pags pa la sgye'u byas pa'i mthu ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-14: des sgye'u de dag ci la byas pa zhib mor byas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-15: bram ze'i bu des ma go'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-16: bram ze de slar 'ongs nas des /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-18: khyod song la chu brog rgyu slongs shig ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-19: des kyang chu brog 'tshal lags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-23: des pha bi khyi sha can te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-24: des khyod la phye byin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-25: de khyod kyis sdig par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-26: zhes smras nas des de la smad pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-27: des zos pa slar bskyugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-30: gang mang po 'chad pa'i bram ze de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-31: da ltar nga nyid yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-32: de'i tshe de'i dus na bram ze'i bu de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-33: da ltar gyi dge slong sh'a ri'i bu ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-34: de'i tshe na yang ngas zas pa la rab tu smad nas de slar bskyugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-35: da 'dir yang ngas zas zos pa la smad nas 'dir yang slar bskyugs par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:244b-36: gleng gzhi ni rgyal po'i khab na ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-0: de'i tshes na rgyal po'i khab kyi grong khyer na khyim bdag me @245a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-1: skyes kyi sring mo'i khyo gcer bu pa'i dge bsnyen dpal sbed ces bya ba zhig 'dug ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-2: khyim bdag me skyes dad pa des 'di snyam du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-3: dpal sbed 'di dge 'dun dag la yon 'bul du bskul lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-4: snyam bsam nas des de la dpal sbed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-7: khyod kyi bsod nams su 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-9: dpal sbed kyis smras pa; ngas kyang dge 'dun dag mchod cing yon dbul bar bya'o /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-10: khyod kyis kyang gang po la sogs te rab tu byung ba'i dge 'dun dag la mchod cing bshos gsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-11: me skyes kyis 'di snyam du bsam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-12: de ste khas ma blangs na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-13: dpal sbed kyis dge 'dun la mchod pa'i bar chad du 'gyur na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-14: sems can thams cad la sbyin pa lta nyes med kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-15: gcer bu pa'i dge 'dun dag la zan byin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-16: bdag gis des dge 'dun la mchod cing yon dbul ba'i ched du bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-17: snyam bsam nas des zan sbyin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-18: zhes khas blangs nas dpal sbed kyis 'di snyam du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-19: bdag gis dang por sangs rgyas la sogs te dge slong gi dge 'dun dag sngar bshos gsol na ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-20: me skyes kyis phyis zan mi sbyin gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-21: gang po la sogs te rab tu byung ba'i dge 'dun dag bshos sngar gsol ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-23: snyam bsam nas me skyes la 'di skad ces smras so /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-24: khyod kyis dang po zan byin cig dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245a-25: ngas kyang phyis dge slong go'u ta ma dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-0: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun @245b dag la zan sbyin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-1: des kyang khas blangs nas de nas khyim bdag me skyes kyis gang po dag gang na 'dug pa der phyin nas gang po dang lhan cig rab tu dga' zhing mgu ba'i gtam sna tshogs dag byas nas phyogs gcig tu 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-2: phyogs gcig tu 'dug nas khyim bdag me skyes kyis gang po la 'di skad ces smras so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-4: khyod sang bdag gi khyim du gcer bu pa mang po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-5: dge 'dun dang lhan cig tu bshos gsol gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-9: gor ma chag par dge sbyong go'u ta ma la sun par gyur nas bdag cag la rab tu dad par gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-10: de ni bdag cag gi rnyed pa rab tu rnyed pa ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-11: gang po bdag cag gi dge 'dun gyi rigs la rab tu dad par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-12: snyam nas des khas blangs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-13: de nas khyim bdag me skyes de dag spyan drangs nas song ngo; ;de nas khyim bdag me skyes kyis de'i nub mo rab tu bsod pa'i bza' ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-14: bca' ba'i kha zas dag sbyar nas nang par sngar langs te sngar langs nas stan bting /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-15: ril ba dag chus bkang ste bzhag nas gang po dag la spyan 'dren pas dus gsol pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-20: dpal sbed kyis de'i gan du 'ongs te smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-22: dge sbyong go'u ta ma ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-23: khyim bdag gi khyim du bzhud de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:245b-24: de nang du bzhud kar sgo'i them pa la zhabs bzhag nas 'dzum pa ston te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-1: dga' bo zhes bya bas stod g-yogs phyogs gcig tu gzar /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-2: pus mo g-yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs te thal mo sbyar nas de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-3: de bzhin gshegs pa'i nyan thos dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-5: rkyen ma mchis par 'dzum pa mi mdzad na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-9: 'dzum pa mdzad ces zhus pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-15: de bzhin gshegs pa'i nyan thos dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-16: rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa ston par mi mdzad de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-17: ji lta bur dgongs pa bzhin lung ston to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-18: zhes smras nas de la skye bo mang po dag kyang rab tu dad par gyur gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-19: khyod kyis kyang khyim bdag me skyes kyi khyim du 'gro ba'i tshe de ltar bya ba'i rigs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-20: 'on kyang skye bo mang po dag rab tu dad par 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-22: de nas gang po gcer bu pa mang pos bskor nas khyim bdag me skyes kyi khyim du phyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-23: khyim bdag me skyes kyi sgo'i them pa la rkang pa bzhag ste rta gad du bgad pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-24: de'i nang nas gcer bu pa zhig gis rkang pa la btud de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246a-25: bcom ldan 'das skyes bu dam pa khyod lta bu rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa mi mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-0: chu bo dregs bral gyi 'gram na spre'u pho zhig gis spre'u mo zhig mthong nas de la sems rab tu chags te spre'u mo de la brgal @246b lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-2: dred de shing gi rtse mo nas rdeg 'chos nas dus 'das so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-3: de'i tshe na nga 'di snyam du sems te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-5: 'dod pa'i rgyus sdug bsngal ba cher gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-7: de skad du kha nas byung ma thag tu khyim bdag me skyes kyis thos nas des bsam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-8: bu zan mo'i bu gang po ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-9: khab 'tshong pa slar khab rdung pa'i khyim du khab tshong par sems pa bzhin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-10: ci nas 'di la kyal ka zhig bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-11: snyam nas de nas dbyug gu can mang po thams cad bde bar 'dug pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-12: khyim bdag des gtsang zhing bsod pa'i bca' ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-13: bza' bas phor pa bkang nas steng du tshod ma blugs te byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-14: gang po gcig pu la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-15: phor pa'i zhabs su tshod ma blugs nas steng du 'bras kyis g-yogs te byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-16: gcer bu pa phal dag za zhing 'dug pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-18: gor ma chag par des ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-19: nga la ston par dmigs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-20: des tshod ma zhim po dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-21: kha zas bzang po sbyin par bsam mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-22: snyam nas ji tsam tshod ma brims zin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-27: snyam nas des bos nas khyim bdag /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-33: des slar tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-34: mi mthong ba ni mthong bar byed //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-35: mthong bar bya ba mi mthong ste //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-36: dregs bral 'gram gyi spre'u mthong la //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:246b-37: phor bu'i nang ga tshod ma min //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-1: yang de'i gdong bltas pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-2: des phor bu'i zhabs na tshod ma 'dug pa bstan te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-4: khyod kyis chu bo dregs bral gyi 'gram na spre'u 'dug pa ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-6: phor bu'i nang na tshod ma 'dug pa ma mthong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-10: ci nas kyang 'jig rten 'di dang pha rol gnyis kar phan par mi 'gyur ba de ltar sbyin pa'i yon tan brjod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-12: me skyes kyis de skyengs par shes nas sbyin pa'i yon tan brjod pa'i tshe de'i mdun na mi 'dug go //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-13: des zan zos nas sbyin pa'i yon tan bklags pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-14: sbyin bdag gis ni sbyin pa'i dus //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-15: dge sbyong gzhan ni za ba'i dus //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-16: lhag ma gzhan la 'ongs pa'i dus //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-17: bsod nams mi dge yod ma yin //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-18: sgo ba zhig 'dug pa des sbyin pa'i yon tan brjod pa la nyan nyan te thos nas khros pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-19: 'di 'dra ba'i sdig can zan zos pa la srung yang mi nus te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-20: 'di 'dra ba'i sbyin pa'i yon tan lta ga la srid kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-21: bu zan mo'i bu 'di la kyal ka zhig bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-22: snyam nas des 'bras khu bum pa gang sgo drung du pho'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-23: sgo gtan gyi gdang phyed tsam drangs te bzhag pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-24: gcer bu pa phyir byung ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-25: 'bras khu las dred de klad pa sgo gtan la phog nas khrag byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-26: de nas sgo ba des mthong ste tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-27: sgo gtan phyung ba'i dus la bab //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-28: 'bras khu pho ba'i dus bab pas //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-29: mgo bo snad pa'i dus yin gyi //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247a-30: dge dang mi dge'i dus med do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-0: de @247b klad pa la khrag zag bzhin du khyim bdag dpal sbed gang na ba der song ste phyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-1: dpal sbed kyis mthong nas btsun pa gang po /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-2: 'di ci nyes zhes dris pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-4: me skyes kyis 'di 'dra ba'i gnod pa byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-9: ci nas 'di ltar dge sbyong go'u ta ma nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa kho bo'i khyim nas gson bzhin du phyir mi 'byung bar bya'i /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-14: de ste dge sbyong go'u ta ma de thams cad mkhyen pa yin na ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-15: mgron du bos kyang khas len du mi btub bo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-16: de ste thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin na ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-18: snyam du bsam nas bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-19: bcom ldan 'das dang lhan cig tu dga' ba'i gtam sna tshogs byas nas phyogs gcig tu 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-20: phyogs gcig tu 'dug nas khyim bdag dpal sbed kyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-21: bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-23: sang bdag gi khyim du dge slong gi dge 'dun dang lhan cig bshos la gshegs par zhal gyis bzhes shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-26: gang gis nga las bden pa mthong bar 'gyur ba de 'di ltar byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:247b-27: de ste ngas khas ma blangs na ni bden pa'i bar chad dag tu 'gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-1: gshegs par zhal gyis bzhes so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-4: thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-5: de ste thams cad mkhyen pa yin na ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-6: 'di ltar khas mi len pa'i rigs na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-7: ci nas 'di thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du mi 'gyur bar dgra'i lan glan no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-8: snyam nas de nas de'i khyim du song ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-9: de'i khyim gyi sgo khar dong chen po brkos nas nang du shing ka di de'i me mdag dud pa med pas bkang nas de'i steng du rtsvas g-yogs nas sas bkab ste bzhag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-10: dug rnon pos bza' ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-12: de nas me skyes kyi sring mos dpal sbed la jo bo ci zhig mdzad ces dris pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-15: jo bo la dgra su mchis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-17: de ste jo bo khyod kyi dgra bcom ldan 'das yin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-18: mdza' bo su zhig mchis kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-19: jo bo 'di lta bu 'phags pa'i chos ma yin pa'i las bya bar mi rigs par soms shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-21: de nas dpal sbed kyis bsam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-22: 'di'ang me skyes kyi gnyen du 'ong ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-23: dge sbyong go'u ta ma la dad pas na gsang shor bar 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-24: snyam nas des mo mdzod kyi nang du bcug ste sgo lcags bcug ste bzhag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248a-25: gang po la sogs pa gcer bu pa thams cad bos nas ngas dgra gsad pas bltar shog cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-0: dge sbyong go'u ta ma gsad pa'i phyir sgor dong chen po brkos nas nang du seng ldeng gi me mdag gis bkang @248b ste bzhag /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-1: kha zas dang skom gyi nang du dug rnon pos bkang ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-2: de dag yid rab tu dga' nas myur zhing rings su dong ste yang thog gi steng du 'dzegs te 'khod nas deng bdag cag bde bar 'khod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-3: dge sbyong go'u ta ma me'i dong gi nang du ji ltar tshig pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-4: dug rnon pos rab tu zhen pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-5: yan man dus la ji ltar 'gyel ba dag la blta'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-6: dpal sbed kyis gdan bting nas bcom ldan 'das la spyan 'dren pas dus gsol to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-7: go'u ta ma bshos kyang sbyar lags kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-8: kye go'u ta ma dus la bab par dgongs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-9: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-11: khyod song la dge slong dag la 'di skad du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-12: dpal sbed kyi khyim du de bzhin gshegs pa ma gshegs par dge slong su'ang sngar ma 'dong zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-16: zhes tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos bcom ldan 'das la mnyan te dge slong dag la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis dpal sbed kyi khyim du de bzhin gshegs pa ma gshegs par sngar dge slong su'ang ma 'dong zhig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-21: de nas bcom ldan 'das snga dro'i dus sham thabs mnabs /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:248b-22: lhung bzed dang chos gos bsnams te dge slong mang pos bskor nas dge slong gi dge 'dun gyis mdun du byas te dpal sbed kyi khyim ga na bar de logs su gshegs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-0: de nas 'od ma'i tshal na gnas @249a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-1: pa'i lha bran rnams sdug bsngal zhing yid mi dga' bas gzir te myur zhing rings par bcom ldan 'das gang na ba der song ste phyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la gtugs te snying rje ba'i tshig gis 'di skad du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-4: dpal sbed kyi khyim du gshegs par mi rigs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-8: de na gnod pa ci zhig yod /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-11: bcom ldan 'das la ma rung par bgyi ba'i slad du bshams so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-16: gnod pa thams cad dang bral na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-17: des nga la gnod pa ci zhig byar yod /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-20: bcom ldan 'das des dgrongs pa'i slad du dong chen po'i nang du seng ldeng gi me mdag gis bkang ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-26: gti mug gi me dag kyang ye shes kyi chus btab na zhi bar 'gyur na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-27: me'i nang na tha ma des ci zhig byar yod kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-28: mya ngan ma byed par 'dug cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-30: de gcig pu ma lags kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-31: gzhan dag gis kyang bcom ldan 'das dgrongs pa'i slad du bya bar sbyar te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-32: dug rnon po mi bzad pas kha zas dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249a-33: btung ba'i nang du sbyar to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-0: @249b bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-2: dug gi gnyen po ye shes kyis 'dod chags kyi dug dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-4: gti mug gi dug kyang rab tu btang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-7: dug gi nang na tha ma des byar ci zhig yod /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-8: bdag slar log la bdag gi las la nan tan du byos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-9: de nas bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab tu byon pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-10: rgyal po'i khab na gnas pa'i lha dag gis snga ma bzhin du gsol pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-11: lha de dag la bcom ldan 'das kyis lha snga ma bzhin du bsgos te slar bkye'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-12: de nas dpal sbed kyi khang pa'i sgor byon pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-13: dpal sbed kyi khyim gyi lhas snga ma bzhin du gsol pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis lha de dag kyang snga ma bzhin du bsgos te slar bkye'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-15: de nas dpal sbed kyi chung mas bsam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-17: bcom ldan 'das sgo dang por phyin cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-19: dong gi steng du zhabs bzhag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-21: dong gi kha rtsvas g-yogs pa'i steng nas lhung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-23: bcom ldan 'das me'i nang du lhung nas dud pas kyang 'tshal /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-25: me lces chos gos tshig pa'i dud pa yang byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-26: snyam nas mi dga' ba des khang pa'i nang du bcug pas yid mi dga' ba skyes nas mig mchi mas gang zhing ngo 'dzum gnas nas rtags mi dge ba la rtog ste ngu zhing 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:249b-28: sems can thams cad la phan pa la rab tu 'jug pa'i yid kyis sgo bar mar byon nas me dong gi steng du zhabs bzhag pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-1: nas me'i dong gi steng du zhabs bzhag ma thag tu de thams cad mtshe'u padma can du gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-5: punda r'i ka dag gis ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-8: ngur pa la sogs pa chu na spyod pa'i bya rnams kyis brgyan te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-9: bya de dag kyang skad sna tshogs 'byin pa ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-10: ji ltar lha'i rdzing man da ka bzhin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-11: nam mkha' la gnas pa'i lha dag gis kyang lha'i me tog ku mu da dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-12: lha'i me tog kha tog dang ldan pas steng nas gtor to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-13: de nas bcom ldan 'das padma'i snying po'i steng dag tu zhabs bzhag ste dpal sbed kyi khyim du byon pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-14: khyim bdag dpal sbed ngo mtshar che ba'i mig gis bgrad de bltas nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-16: bcom ldan 'das kyi rdzu 'phrul dang cho 'phrul la ltos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-18: gang po mi dga' ba'i bzhin du bsgyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-20: dge slong go'u ta ma dad dam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-21: de'i sgyu ma la dad dam zhes smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-24: de ltar 'di lta bus bsgrub tu rung na ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-25: khyod kyang thams cad mkhyen pa na sgyu ma de lta bu byos la ston cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-28: phu nu dag kyang bsgrub par gyis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-30: dgos pa ma grub par gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250a-32: snyam nas des de la spyos te khang pa'i steng nas babs te skyengs nas bcom ldan 'das la mngon du 'byung bar ma nus te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-0: de @250b nas 'gros dal zhing bags kyis song nas gdong yang sa la bltas te dpal sbed kyi khyim nas byung ste bros te song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-1: de nas khyim bdag dpal sbed khyim bdag me skyes kyi sring mo gang na ba der song ste phyin nas sgo lcags phye ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs la phyag tshol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-7: snyam nas snying rje ba'i tshig gis dal bus smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-8: sdig pa'i grogs pos bslus te bsad na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-9: bdag la bgam du ci zhig yod ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-11: bzang mo bden par zer te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-14: bcom ldan 'das dgrongs par ma nus pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-15: bcom ldan 'das la mngon du 'byung bar mi nus kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-16: nga khrid la song zhig ces smras pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-17: des dpal sbed kyi chung ma de dga' ba skyes nas mgu ba'i yid kyis dpal sbed khrid de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-18: bcom ldan 'das gang na ba der song nas phyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-19: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-23: mi dge ba'i grogs pos bslus pas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-24: bcom ldan 'das la mi dge ba'i rnam pa 'di lta bu dag bgyis so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-26: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis glang po che'i sna 'dra ba'i phyag brkyangs nas gsungs pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:250b-29: de bzhin gshegs pa la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-1: bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-2: mdza' ba dang dgrar bye brag mi 'byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-4: zhes smras pa dang; de nas khyim bdag dpal sbed de bzhin gshegs pa la rab tu dga' ba skyes nas mos pa'i yid kyis bcom ldan 'das la cung zad cig gzhes shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-5: bdag gis bshos de gdod sbyar ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-9: de bzhin gshegs pa la spyan 'dren pas dus gsol to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-10: go'u ta ma bshos dag sbyar lags kyi; kye go'u ta ma dus mkhyen par mdzod cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-17: mi dge ba'i grogs po la bltas par gyur pa'i blos log par lta ba gsum du 'gro ba'i sdig pas de la gzhol te kun la sdug par 'gro ba gnyis kyang bgags nas bcom ldan 'das la gnod par bya ba'i phyir zhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-22: gnod pa thams cad dang bral na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-23: ci'i phyir nga la gnod par 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-25: bdag gis dug rnon pos zhal zas dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-26: skyems kyi nang du sbyar gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-27: de dag pho la gdod sbyar ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251a-29: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-2: gti mug gi dug kyang rab tu bskyugs shing bor na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-3: dug ngan pa 'di lta bus ci zhig byar yod kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-4: gang sbyar ba de khyer te shog cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-5: de nas bcom ldan 'das dge slong gi dge 'dun gyi mdun du gdan bting ba la bzhugs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-6: bzhugs nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-8: song la dge slong dag la 'di skad du /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-9: nam rgan rim du 'byor tshogs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-10: zhes skad ma byung gi bar du su yang zan ma za zhig par sgos shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-11: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos dge slong dag la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-15: zhes skad ma byung gi bar du su'ang ma za zhig ces byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-16: de nas dge slong gi dge 'dun dag bde bar 'khod nas kha zas dag bsnyen pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-18: cho 'phrul gyis dpal sbed kyi khyim rgan rim du 'byor tshogs zhes skad phyung ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-20: skom dag kyang dug med par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-21: dpal sbed de dogs bzhin du kha zas dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-23: rgan rim nas gzhon nu dag gi drung du 'ongs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-24: da tsam dge slong rgan rim dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-25: dug rnon pos 'gyel gor ma chag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-26: gzhon nu nas yang rgan rim gyi drung du 'ongs nas yang 'di snyam du sems te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-27: de'i blo yang de lta bur skyes nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:251b-31: gti mug gi dug spangs kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-1: thos thams cad ma yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-3: de ltar dge slong thams cad kyis bshos gsol na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-4: gcig la yang gnod par ma gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-6: de'i lhag ma zos pa dag la yang gnod par ma gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-7: de nas khyim bdag dpal sbed phyi phyir dad pa skyes so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-8: de chung ma dang gnyis kyis bcom ldan 'das bshos gsol nas lhung bzed phyung ste phyag bcabs par shes nas stan dma' ba zhig blangs te bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar chos nyan pa'i phyir 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-9: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dpal sbed dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-13: rang bzhin dag mkhyen nas 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi'i chos rab tu rtogs par 'gyur ba de lta bu bshad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-14: khyim bdag dpal sbed kyis de thos nas 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo nyi shu ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom nas rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu mngon du byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-15: des bden pa mthong nas dga' ba'i tshig lan gsum smras te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis phan btags pa 'di lta bu ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-18: bdag la phas kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-24: rgyal pos kyang ma bgyis lhas kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-25: snga ma'i pha mes dag gis ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-26: dge sbyong dang bram ze dag gis kyang ma bgyis te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252a-27: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag gis mchi ma dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-0: bskams @252b rus pa'i ri las ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-9: zhes smras nas yang gsol pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-10: nyes pa mang ba ma rungs pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-11: ngan du 'gro ba'i lam rnams te //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-12: khyod kyi mthus ni de dag bcad /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-13: mtho ris 'gro ba'i sgo phye bsod nams can //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-14: mya ngan 'da' ba'i lam yang bdag gis thob //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-15: khyod la brten pas thob pa nyes bral ba'i /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-16: bdag gi mig ni dag cing rnam par dag /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-17: 'phags pa dgyes pa'i gnas bzhi thob //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-18: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho pha rol brgal //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-19: skye bo lha min lha dang mis mchod pa //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-20: skye ba na ba rga shi rnam par bral //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-21: srid pa stong du'ang rnyed par shin tu dka'//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-22: thub pa khyod mthong dang ni 'bras bur ldan //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-30: dge slong gi dge 'dun du skyabs su mchi'i /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-31: deng phan chad nam 'tsho'i bar srog dang yang bsngos te skyabs su mchi nas mngon du dad kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-32: bdag dge bsnyen du zungs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-34: deng phan chad mu stegs can gcer bu pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-36: gcer bu pa'i nyan thos rnams la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-38: bcom ldan 'das kyi nyan thos dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:252b-44: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis khyim bdag dpal sbed la chos kyi gtam gyis yang dag par bstan /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:253a-1: rab tu dga' bar byas nas gdan las bzhengs te bzhud do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:253a-2: de nas bcom ldan 'das gtsug lag khang du byon nas dge slong gi dge 'dun gyi mdun du gdan bting pa la bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:253a-3: bzhugs nas bcom ldan 'das kyi dge slong dag la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:253a-5: khyim bdag dpal sbed kyi khyim du de lta bu'i gnod pa dag byung ba de la der de bzhin gshegs pas mkhyen par ma gyur na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:253a-6: gor ma chag par dge slong rab tu mang po zhig dug gis dus 'das par 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-013-001:253a-7: khyim bdag de'ang ngan du spyad pas mtshams med pa'i sems can dmyal bar ltung ngo //
